text: Angel Diaz is the name of: == People in sports == * Ángel Luis Rodríguez Díaz (born 1987), Spanish football (soccer) player * Ángel Gastón Díaz (born 1981), Argentine football (soccer) player * Angel Díaz, Guatemalan decathlete who, among other things, competed in the 1983 World Championships in Athletics – Men's decathlon == People in public service == * Ángel Romero Díaz (born 1979), social worker, politician, and writer-journalist from Spain * Ángel Díaz de Entresotos (1927–2009), late Spanish politician and former President of Cantabria == Other people == * Ángel Nieves Díaz (1951–2006), American convict * Ángel Díaz (singer) (1929–1998), singer of Argentine tangos : (in Spanish customs for surnames: the first name is the family surname; the second name is the family surname)
title: Angel Diaz
